title: match history
body: match history hasnt been working in browser for me for awhile, idk if its just me.  is this being addressed?

replies.body: Yeah this has been a problem for me too for the past few weeks. matchhistory.na.leagueoflegends.com just gives me a white blank box on all my computers on all my browsers, and for all of my friends. And matchhistory.euw.leagueoflegends.com works fine for me so I just feel like the NA match history is completely down or something. Hope there's a fix.
I've also had some issues with loading match history. I've tried using a different browser and incognito mode. (different browser that was used is the dreaded internet explorer)

This can sometimes happen depending on your web browser or add-ons. Below is a list of things you can try to resolve this:

* Clear your Browser cache/data with [this guide.](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies)
* Try a *private or incognito* mode in your browser, as this disables most problematic add-ons.
* Try using a completely different browser.

Let me know if one of those work for you.
